---
title: Creepy Cottage Pie with Cheesy Potato Top and Peas
description: This Creepy Cottage Pie is a crowd pleaser and is one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R10_W41_UK_R17050-3_Main_low-9ee7dccc.jpg
